                               # Ratings:  340
                               # Visits:  4969

   Studentjobs.gov
   http://www.studentjobs.gov/
   Your one stop to find special opportunities for students in the Federal
   government. Learn about co-ops, internships, summer jobs, the
   Outstanding Scholars Program, volunteer opportunities, and plenty of
   part-time and full-time jobs.
   Related Topics: Internships  Student job programs  Environment  Health
   care  Education  Poverty  Children
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  60
                               # Visits:  1183

   National Health Service Corps (NHSC)
   http://www.bphc.hrsa.gov/nhsc
   NHSC's mission is to assign physicians and other health care providers
   to serve in communities with shortages of health professionals. The
   benefits of service can include scholarships and student loan
   repayment. programs.
   Related Topics: Scholarships and grants  Student loans  Health care
   Poverty
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  25
                               # Visits:  788

   Volunteer Service in the Federal Government (Office of Personnel Mgmt)
   http://www.usajobs.opm.gov/EI20.htm
   Federal agencies and departments offer unpaid training opportunities to
   students in high school and college. These opportunities provide work
   experience related to your academic program and allows you to explore
   career options.
   Related Topics: Explore careers  Environment  Health care  Education
   Poverty  Children  International
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  14
                               # Visits:  612

   US Public Health Service Commissioned Corps (US Dept of Health & Human
   Services)
   http://www.usphs.gov
   The Commissioned Corps provides a variety of employment opportunities
   for health professionals and students both throughout the Department of
   Health and Human Services and within other Federal Agencies.
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  Scholarships and grants
   Internships  Job search  Health care
   __________________________________________________________________


