   Peace Corps
   http://www.peacecorps.gov/home.html
   Volunteer with the Peace Corps and make a difference in the global
   community.
   Related Topics: Environment  Health care  Education  Poverty  Children
   International
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  22
                               # Visits:  373

   Jobs and Scholarships -- Indian Health Service (IHS)
   http://www.ihs.gov/JobsCareerDevelop/index.asp
   IHS offers repayment of student loans for those in health professions
   who provide two years of service. Also, check out scholarships for
   American Indian/Alaskan Native health professionals and many job
   postings.
   Related Topics: Scholarships and grants  Health care  Diversity
   __________________________________________________________________


                                  Two Stars
                                # Ratings:  4
                               # Visits:  247

   Centers for Disease Control -- Training & Employment Opportunities
   http://www.cdc.gov/train.htm#empl
   The Centers for Disease Control provides this website with links to a
   variety of training opportunities, including fellowships and research
   programs, along with a link to all CDC employment opportunities.
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  Fellowships  Job search  Health
   care  Housing, health, and the environment
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                                # Ratings:  9
                               # Visits:  186

   Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Admin
   http://www.samhsa.gov/
   SAMHSA's mission is to improve the quality and availability of
   prevention, treatment, and rehab services for substance abuse and
   mental illnesses. Excellent information and links.
   Related Topics: Health care  Housing, health, and the environment
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                               # Ratings:  10
                               # Visits:  157

   Scholarships and Loan Repayment Program (Indian Health Services)
   http://www.ihs.gov/JobscareerDevelop/DHPS/HPRTSC.asp
   Learn about the Indian Health Service's scholarships for American
   Indian health professionals and a loan repayment program in exchange
   for two years of full-time clinical practice at an approved Indian
   health program.
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  Scholarships and grants  Student
   loans  Health care  Diversity
   __________________________________________________________________


                                 Three Stars
                                # Ratings:  4
                               # Visits:  149

   "Put a Face on Homelessness" (HUD)
   http://www.hud.gov/december.cfm
   Put a Face on Homelessness is a public service campaign to help address
   the problem of homelessness. Enter your zip code to get a list of
   providers in your area and volunteer to help.
   Related Topics: Health care  Poverty

